article_id:33,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Treasure Chest Rewards in Co-op,image_path:,message:<div>It has come to our attention that treasure chest rewards sometimes cannot be obtained from defeating bosses in co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Updating to version 1.0.6 (available later today) will make these rewards appear in the battle result screen, even if treasure chests do not appear after defeating a boss.</div><div>We plan to fully address this issue in further updates.</div><div><br></div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will be giving out the following gifts to players who started the game before<span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539605700"></span></div><div><br></div><div>・Quality Honey x5</div><div>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x5</div><div>・Skip Tickets x6</div><div><br></div><div>These items can be received from your goodie box upon login until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540210500"></span>.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(184, 49, 47);">Note: Skip Tickets from the daily login bonus will be discarded if you already have 30 tickets (the maximum amount) when trying to receive them.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1539605700,update_time1539606958